        .description
          .title Description

          p After a trip through the Milky Way, your crew is ready to return to Earth. However, a terrible storm of asteroids and debris block your path. During your trip, you notice that the inertia and gravitational pull are constantly reversing. Navigate your way through this anomaly so that you can tell Earth of your findings!
          
          p How to play:
          ol
            li Tap your finger on the screen where you want your ship to go.
            li Don't go off the screen or hit an piece of debris! If you do, your ship will be destroyed.
            li Have fun!
        
        .features
          .sHeader2 Built-on
          ul
            li PhaserJS
            li Ludei Cloud